Hospital Management System
New Record To insert a new record simply click on New Record. This section contains four options. - Patient: After successfully saving the Patient record a Payment record related to it automatically will be created. - Doctor: First add the Doctor record and then below that you will be able to define unique Specializations for that doctor. - Appointment: For defining the upcoming Appointments. - Department: This is where you can define the Departments of the hospital, clinkc, etc
Edit Record To edit some records you can use the Edit Record tab. - Patient: Updating thing that need to be change. - Doctor: Beside the Doctor record, it is possible to add, edit or remove any Specialization. - Department: In case of any typos in defining.
Appointments This is where the upcoming Appointments are shown. By leaving the texts for searching empty, it shows all upcoming Appointments ordered by date. In Appointment manager there are some features to change the appointment time and date or changing its state to canceled or completed.
Prescription: This tab is for storing the Medicines of a completed Appointment. keep in mind that you cannot define a Prescription when an appointment is canceled or not completed.
Payment: This is the Patient's Payment tab that shows the Payment information on each patient. The information can also be updated.
Remove Record This tab is useful for removing some unwanted and wrong records. - Patient: You can delete Patient in here. The records can either get deleted permanently or not. Keep in mind that for storing purposes, a Patient record that had Appointments before, can't be deleted. When a Patient record is removed completely the assigned Payment record will be deleted too. - Doctor: Same as the removing Patient process, Doctor records can be deleted permanently but only in case of not having any Appointments yet. Also as a Doctor record removes, the related Specializations will be deleted too. - Department: In case of environmental changes this feature has been created. - Appointments: In this section only canceled Appointments can be deleted.
About And here it is! The about page.
